%section#how-to
  .wrapper

    %h2 How To

    To get started with Hound.cc, all you have to do is send us an email!

    %ul
      %li Compose a new email
      %li
        Include [time format]@hound.cc in the To/Cc/Bcc field(s)
        %ul
          %li
            %span To: or Cc:
            Hound sends a reminder to you (the sender) and
            the other recipients (if any).
          %li
            %span Bcc:
            Hound only sends you a reminder.

    %h3 Time Formats

    Hound has a simple (yet powerful) time formatting scheme;

    %h4 From Now

    %ul
      %li= mail_to '2minutes@hound.cc'
      %li= mail_to '3hours@hound.cc'
      %li= mail_to '1day@hound.cc'
      %li= mail_to '2weeks@hound.cc'
      %li= mail_to '3months@hound.cc'

    %h4 Composite
    %ul
      %li
        = mail_to '1day2hours@hound.cc'

    %h4 Weekdays
    %ul
      %li= mail_to 'friday@hound.cc'
      %li= mail_to 'nexttuesday@hound.cc'
      %li= mail_to 'nextweek@hound.cc'

    %h4 Handy
    %ul
      %li
        = mail_to 'tomorrow@hound.cc'
        (8am tomorrow)
      %li
        = mail_to 'endofday@hound.cc'
        (5pm today)

    %h4 Actual Date
    %ul
      %li

    %h4 Abbreviations
    %ul
      %li
        = mail_to '2m@hound.cc'
        (2 minutes)
      %li
        = mail_to '1mo@hound.cc'
        (1 month)
      %li
        = mail_to 'tom@hound.cc'
        (tomorrow)

